{"tid":2402204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK ROSÉ 將在3月發行SOLO專輯！投入歷代級製作費＋規模很大的MV！","createTime":"2021-02-10T09:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:42:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f49dbf8aa1fcf2d1fe89a3846b8764742bca305","tid":2402204,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_66ae7dbfd3372890c12803e0adf0e4bc/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-10/133639-896779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_66ae7dbfd3372890c12803e0adf0e4bc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-10%2F133639-896779.jpg&h=0264f6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日（10），有相關人士透露：「ROS&Eacute;將在3月發行個人專輯。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，YG方面也回應：「ROS&Eacute;正在進行SOLO準備，將會通過正式公告發表具體回歸日程。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK成員ROS&Eacute;在上月31日舉行的線上演唱會《THE SHOW》上公開SOLO曲《GONE》。YG當時也表示：「ROS&Eacute;的SOLO專輯主打歌MV拍攝已全部結束，由於投入歷代級製作費、規模也很大，為了提高完整度，正在盡全力進行後期工作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b78cc60dfe78df5d16d2cc71fbac89de/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-10/133639-896774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b78cc60dfe78df5d16d2cc71fbac89de%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-10%2F133639-896774.jpg&h=eefae7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5c1413ad0c0f644d1d71514ffe2de5d9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-10/133639-896775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5c1413ad0c0f644d1d71514ffe2de5d9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-10%2F133639-896775.jpg&h=911a9a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：IG@roses_are_rosie）<br />\n<br />\n她的SOLO預告影片在上月25日公開，僅僅33秒卻讓人忍不住重複播放，歌詞唱著：「我的愛已逝去，我的愛已逝去，而你也跟著在我心裡消亡。」讓粉絲們更加期待全曲，不到一個月的時間，影片也已經突破3800萬點擊。<br />\n<br />\n而ROS&Eacute;的SOLO出道也引發國內外關注，美國知名雜誌《富比士》（Forbes）網頁上，專業人士預測今年度在美國能夠成功的五位 K-POP SOLO歌手，ROS&Eacute;就是之一。也希望YG可以公佈相關消息啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9cece33195675929fc59e44095200909/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-10/133639-896776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9cece33195675929fc59e44095200909%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-10%2F133639-896776.jpg&h=df68222b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c4db91172bbd00b3894713a97365cf4d51dcec0","tid":2402204,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"點可以唔撐...！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2261d2b4010a118c1add034f6f8b799ae46aca0b","tid":2402204,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c4db91172bbd00b3894713a97365cf4d51dcec0","tid":2402204,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"點可以唔撐...！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"睇定d先!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a51dbcfe221a1425d2ac6e35010b5d20d75de4","tid":2402204,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2261d2b4010a118c1add034f6f8b799ae46aca0b","tid":2402204,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c4db91172bbd00b3894713a97365cf4d51dcec0","tid":2402204,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"點可以唔撐...！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"睇定d先!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"你25...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c278187388d7f1f09e4128a935144aead95fa","tid":2402204,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c4db91172bbd00b3894713a97365cf4d51dcec0","tid":2402204,"uid":